				<div class='chart'>
					<p class='chart__copy'>Although women in Massachusetts make up a smaller proportion of binge and heavy drinkers than men, the female population saw larger increases from 2005 to 2012. Female binge drinkers rose <mark class='mark--binge'>25.8 percent</mark> and heavy drinkers <mark class='mark--heavy'>31.8 percent</mark>, while males rose <mark class='mark--binge'>6 percent</mark> and <mark class='mark--heavy'>13.9 percent</mark>, respectively.</p>
